query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(tag site) NoMergeJoin(site tag tag_question question) */ select count(*)
from tag AS tag
inner join site AS site
on tag.site_id = site.site_id AND tag.name = 'java' AND site.site_name = 'stackoverflow'
inner join tag_question AS tag_question
on tag_question.tag_id = tag.id AND tag_question.site_id = site.site_id
inner join question AS question
on tag_question.question_id = question.id AND question.site_id = site.site_id;
